<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-16515] camel-github component possible OOM due to only adding elements to an unbuonded map</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16515</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I think there is a potential for OOM errors here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/components/camel-github/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/github/consumer/CommitConsumer.java#L68&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/components/camel-github/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/github/consumer/CommitConsumer.java#L68&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;basically each commit sha is added to an in memory list of already processed commits used as an idempotent inmemory repository, but elements in the map are never removed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
